            <img class="testimonial-logo" src="/assets/customers/png/siguna.png" alt="Siguna" />
            <img class="testimonial-photo" src="/assets/photos/testimonial-siguna.jpg" alt="Siguna team" />
            <p class="testimonial-quote">"We have chosen Fished as our order management provider because they offer a modern and flexible solution tailored to the needs of the seafood industry, while also giving us better oversight, traceability, and more efficient work processes."</p>
            <div class="testimonial-author"><div><strong>Evgenia Kozlova</strong><span>CEO, Siguna</span></div></div>
          </div>
          <div class="testimonial-card">
            <img class="testimonial-logo" src="/assets/customers/png/nordic-wildfish.png" alt="Nordic Wildfish" />
            <img class="testimonial-photo" src="/assets/photos/testimonial-nordicwildfish.webp" alt="Nordic Wildfish team" />
            <p class="testimonial-quote">"Fished works great &#8212; it's both intuitive and functional. My favourite features are the universal search field, pallet tracking and the ability to easily correct my own mistakes &#8212; all of which make my daily work more efficient."</p>
            <div class="testimonial-author"><div><strong>Elisabeth Myklebust</strong><span>Logistics &amp; Export Coordinator, Nordic Wildfish</span></div></div>
